How will you reduce costs?
Archive old data to Blob Storage; use Cosmos DB only for recent records.

How will your solution serve archived data?
Azure Function with fallback logic to fetch from Blob if not in Cosmos DB.

How will you ensure APIs remain unchanged?
Internal fallback logic maintains the same API contract.

What tools did you use?
Terraform, Azure Functions, Cosmos DB, Blob Storage, Data Factory.

What bonus features are implemented?
Automated archival, architecture diagram, IaC, CI/CD ready.
